Paper: hep-th/9405065

Date: 1994-05-10

Title: Supergravity and the quest for a unified theory

Authors: Sergio Ferrara

Comments: 15 pages, latex

A recollection of some theoretical developments that preceded and followedthe first formulation of supergravity theory is presented. Special emphasis isplaced on the impact of supergravity on the search for a unified theory offundamental interactions.